snippet: Sukhoi, which makes the Superjet 100, said it expected 40 new orders for the passenger plane even after the crash of a demonstration model in May.
abstract: Russian jet maker Sukhoi, which produces the Superjet 100, says it expects 40 new orders for the passenger plane even after the crash of a demonstration model in May.
lead_paragraph: Sukhoi, which makes the Superjet 100, said it expected 40 new orders for the passenger plane even after the crash of a demonstration model in May.

headline.main: New Russian Jet Garners Orders Despite Crash
headline.print_headline: Russian Jet Maker Says Crash Hasn’t Hurt Orders
